        <num>37-0507</num>
        <heading>Product labeling</heading>
        <content>
          <p>ยง 37-0507. Product labeling.\n  The commissioner may authorize product labeling of products that do\nnot contain bisphenol A. The label on such products may prominently\nstate "Bisphenol A Free" or "BPA-Free" to inform consumers that the\nproduct does not contain the chemical bisphenol A.\n</p>
